column16: Jose Altuve grounds into a force out, third baseman Eduardo Escobar to second baseman Brian Dozier.   George Springer out at 2nd.
Jake Marisnick doubles (2) on a ground ball to left fielder Eddie Rosario.   Marwin Gonzalez scores.    Norichika Aoki scores.  Fielding error by left fielder Eddie Rosario.
Norichika Aoki grounds into a force out, shortstop Jorge Polanco to second baseman Brian Dozier.   Marwin Gonzalez to 3rd.    Yuli Gurriel out at 2nd.    Norichika Aoki to 1st.
Alex Bregman lines out to right fielder Max Kepler.
Yuli Gurriel walks.   Marwin Gonzalez to 2nd.
Marwin Gonzalez singles on a fly ball to right fielder Max Kepler.
Evan Gattis homers (4) on a line drive to left field.
Carlos Beltran lines out to shortstop Jorge Polanco.
Carlos Correa singles on a line drive to left fielder Eddie Rosario.   Josh Reddick scores.    Jose Altuve to 2nd.
Jose Altuve singles on a ground ball to shortstop Jorge Polanco.   George Springer scores.    Josh Reddick to 3rd.  Throwing error by shortstop Jorge Polanco.
Josh Reddick walks.   George Springer to 2nd.
George Springer singles on a soft ground ball to first baseman Joe Mauer.
Alex Bregman lines out to center fielder Byron Buxton.
Yuli Gurriel grounds out sharply, third baseman Ehire Adrianza to first baseman Joe Mauer.
Marwin Gonzalez grounds into a double play, shortstop Jorge Polanco to second baseman Brian Dozier to first baseman Joe Mauer.   Brian McCann out at 2nd.
Carlos Beltran lines out to left fielder Eddie Rosario.
